{"tid":1399766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 對付軍政府方法","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T10:02:47.000Z","uid":271051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"83f2364d553af4c5a93bb3aeaf76e94541b136f9","tid":1399766,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbeb051896e0b9fa17c3db76981af38b935a75b","tid":1399766,"uid":190521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"拒絕成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n一成立，一來有人會收貨，場運動會慢慢散<br />\n二來，一定會不了了之，因分分鐘係軍政府自己查返自己"},{"pid":"78c2acae2f8a683009e39e30c62ce22fe8209f88","tid":1399766,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bbeb051896e0b9fa17c3db76981af38b935a75b","tid":1399766,"uid":190521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"拒絕成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n一成立，一來有人會收貨，場運動會慢慢散<br />\n二來，一定會不了了之，因分分鐘係軍政府自己查返自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"咁之後呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5046018b62f1c5f0bd43a365826d92b171d3fc36","tid":1399766,"uid":190521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/715154608933977/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347501365699305%2Fposts%2F715154608933977%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsQuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=7ada7091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/715154608933977/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>究竟警察是否公務員</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n張建宗代表警察向市民道歉，然後多名警員指責張建宗示弱。其後，張再向警察道歉澄清。<br />\n<br />\n未幾，張又對參與罷工的公務員發言，認為公務員需要與政府持相同意見。那麼，為何警察又可以持相反意見？警察是政府公務員嗎？<br />\n<br />\n答案是警察正打算搶奪香港政府的權力，成為香港軍政府。而張建宗是公務員，因此率先表演可謂沒有與政府持相反意見，向軍政府道歉，並且勸告其他公務員。<br />\n<br />\n而軍政府，也開始對各方面行使管治權。包括對網上罷工表是遺憾（經濟範疇），對充公一般工業用頭盔（貿易範疇），對港鐵要求不停站（運輸範疇），對醫院電腦資料的蒐集（醫療範疇）。以往，需要跨部門的工作，軍政府一手包辦，甚至代替其他部門發言。<br />\n<br />\n很快，軍政府會騎劫特首。香港管治不了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>要香的你重回正軌，<span style=\"color: red;\">最少要經歷一連串混亂</span>，使現在的港共政府徹底崩壞，然後才能有國會普選和元首普選的新香港政府。</strong><br />\n<br />\n現在放棄嗎？要獨立調查委員會嗎？你就會獲得一個香港軍政府統治。香港人必須奮勇下去。不建國，就滅族！這場戰爭打下去！<br />\n<br />\n香港軍政府發言<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357791&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsQuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=2bc6a8e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357791&h=cd818733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357791</a>"},{"pid":"d08d10dcd03ca7a0050451ca2da9d92fbeb4180e","tid":1399766,"uid":92442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"香港得三萬隻狗<br />\n每個人至少識一隻<br />\n每個人搞掂自己識嗰隻<br />\n只要三萬人代價就可以搞掂軍政府"},{"pid":"cf0ad843766e3f0ebb3513931053538385a8db77","tid":1399766,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08d10dcd03ca7a0050451ca2da9d92fbeb4180e","tid":1399766,"uid":92442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"香港得三萬隻狗<br />\n每個人至少識一隻<br />\n每個人搞掂自己識嗰隻<br />\n只要三萬人代價就可以搞掂軍政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"由明轉暗係唯一出路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de1299640451b447aa6488c4198232c3dd70b58","tid":1399766,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}